{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2014/11/7/interactive-light-sculptures/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://blog.aboutme.be"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b7fcf77b-ccdc-5e53-b095-ee420c10315b","excerpt":"After last year’s elevator pitch I was invited back to gave a full talk this year. I wanted to elaborate on javascript and hardware interaction, while linking…","html":"<p>After <a href=\"/2013/09/05/500-people-controlled-my-arduino-at-reasons-to-be-creative-2013/\">last year’s elevator pitch</a> I was invited back to gave a full talk this year. I wanted to elaborate on javascript and hardware interaction, while linking everything to a general theme. I went for “physical workouts”, and built some demos that had to do with that.</p>\n<p>During my talk, I covered different libraries &#x26; hardware platforms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bluetooth LE &#x26; <a href=\"https://github.com/noble/noble\">the noble library</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pulsesensor.com/\">Pulse Sensor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sparkdevices/spark-core-wi-fi-for-everything-arduino-compatible\">Spark Core</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://johnny-five.io/\">Johnny-five</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cylonjs.com/\">Cylon.JS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tessel.io/\">Tessel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.spacebrew.cc/\">Spacebrew</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>I wanted to keep things fun and interactive for the audience as well. So I invited people on stage to play heartrate controlled games and dance mat challenges. All built using javascript!</p>\n<p>The people from AnalogFolk captured a nice video of one of the demos:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/105886639\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen style=\" position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \"></iframe> </div>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://github.com/wouterverweirder/javascript-workout\">find my presentation and demos on Github</a>. Enjoy!</p>","fields":{"slug":"/2014/11/7/interactive-light-sculptures/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript workout at Reasons to be Creative 2014","date":"09 Sep, 2014","description":false,"tags":["reasons to be creative","arduino","nodejs","javascript"],"hasCover":true,"cover":{"publicURL":"/static/6c840fc0e5356653145f910afce9bed5/preview.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='325'%20height='325'%20viewBox='0%200%20325%20325'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%2028v27h3c2%200%203%202%201%202l-1%203-1%202v-6l-1%2063v61l2%201%203-1%2017-2a156%20156%200%200018%200l2%201c3-1%204%200%205%207l2%206%202%202a250%20250%200%20018%2045h-1l-2-1c-3%200-3-2%200-2%202-1%203-3%201-3-1-1-2%200-2%201h-1l-2-1-3-1c-2-2-2-2-5-1s-5%201-5-1h-4l-1%202-2-1c-1-2-1-2-3%200h-6l-2%201v-2l1-2-2%201c-1%202-8-5-8-7l-1-1-2-4-2-2-1-1-4-2H0v113h309l1-3c4-7%206-32%205-50%200-9%201-12%206-15l4-2v35l1-100V56l-3-1c-2%200-4%202-4%205%200%204-1%207-3%208-1%201%200%201%204%201s5%200%205%202l-11%201a424%20424%200%2001-43-2c0-2-1-2-3-2s-2%200-1-4c1-3%200-5-1-3l-3%202-1%201h-3c-2-1-2-2%200-3%201-2%201-2-1-3-3-2-1-9%203-9%201%200%202%205%200%206v2c2%200%204-3%204-8%201-4-2-6-5-4s-7-2-4-4v-4l-1-2v-9l1-1c-1-1%200-4%202-9v-2l1-2v-2l-1-6V0h-11c-9%200-11%200-11%202l1%201v2c-1%203-3%201-2-2%200-3-3-4-4-1l-2%201c-1%200-2%200-1-1%200-2-3-2-24-2h-24l-1%203-1%202V3c0-4-2-4-5-1h-1c1-2-2-2-49-2H73l1%202c1%202%201%203-2%203-3%201-4%200-4-3l1-2H0v28M294%203c1%204-2%206-3%204h-1l-2%201-2%202c0%202%202%203%203%202l3%202%203%202c2%200%204%202%202%202v8c-1%202-2%204-1%205l-1%201c-1-1-3%200-4%202s-4%203-3%201c1-1%200-2-1-3h-1l-2%201c-1%200-1%201%201%203%203%203%203%203%205%202%202-2%202-1%202%204%200%204%201%205%202%204h2l1-1h2l3-1h3l1%202%202-3%20